org.datavec.image.loader

Class NativeImageLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.datavec.image.loader.BaseImageLoader
      • org.datavec.image.loader.NativeImageLoader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AndroidNativeImageLoader, CifarLoader, Java2DNativeImageLoader

    public class NativeImageLoader
extends BaseImageLoader
    Uses JavaCV to load images. Allowed formats: bmp, gif, jpg, jpeg, jp2, pbm, pgm, ppm, pnm, png, tif, tiff, exr, webp
    Author:
    saudet

    Serialized Form
